# game/scripts/day15.rpy:5
translate spanish d15a_b4ceb598:

    # Z "I don't know yet when I will be called upon by the Queen, [A]."
    Z "Aún no sé cuándo me llamará la Reina, [A]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:8
translate spanish d15a_daed793d:

    # A "Do you have any other missions planned?"
    A "¿Tienes otras misiones planeadas?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:11
translate spanish d15a_f294c378:

    # Z "Nothing specific that you need to worr-."
    Z "Nada específico de lo que debas preocuparte..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:15
translate spanish d15a_9a1cb0b0:

    # "The door opens..."
    "La puerta se abre..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:16
translate spanish d15a_b2bcc58d:

    # C3 "Helllooooo?"
    C3 "¿Holaaaaaaaaaaaa?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:19
translate spanish d15a_d0e82685:

    # A "Who...?!"
    A "¡¿Quién...?!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:22
translate spanish d15a_987e3a4b:

    # Na "Ohhh...!"
    Na "¡Ohhh...!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:25
translate spanish d15a_7f09cb7a:

    # Na "[A]?! Is that you?!"
    Na "¡¿[A]?! ¡¿Eres tú?!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:28
translate spanish d15a_26f75938:

    # Na "No way!"
    Na "¡No me lo puedo creer!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:31
translate spanish d15a_80318b4c:

    # A "Uh... wait... is that... Na-"
    A "Uh... espera... es que... Na-"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:34
translate spanish d15a_9b6d22bf:

    # A "Wahhh!"
    A "¡Queee!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:35
translate spanish d15a_dcaf55de:

    # Na "Cousinnn!!!"
    Na "¡¡¡Primaaaa!!!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:38
translate spanish d15a_76e9b805:

    # Na "[A]! It's been so long!"
    Na "¡[A]! ¡Ha pasado tanto tiempo!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:39
translate spanish d15a_e86826ff:

    # A "Is that... really you, Nadia?"
    A "¿Eres... realmente tú, Nadia?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:42
translate spanish d15a_224b9537:

    # Na "Of course it's me! Or do we have other cousins I don't know about?"
    Na "¡Por supuesto que soy yo! ¿O tenemos otras primas que yo no conozca?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:43
translate spanish d15a_d1aaf1eb:

    # A "Wow, you're so..."
    A "Guau, eres tan..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:46
translate spanish d15a_8d0b4a90:

    # Na "Hey uncle, what's up..."
    Na "Ey tío, ¿qué pasa..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:53
translate spanish d15a_ec1b1c7c:

    # Na "Mom and I decided to visit. Well I decided, and she told me I couldn't come alone..."
    Na "Mamá y yo decidimos venir de visita. Bueno, yo lo decidí y ella me dijo que no podía venir sola..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:54
translate spanish d15a_d5df170d:

    # Z "Your mother is here?"
    Z "¿Tu madre está aquí?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:55
translate spanish d15a_1e2dd1e8:

    # Na "Wild, right? Stuffy Rabiah has left the safety of the city walls!"
    Na "Salvaje, ¿verdad? ¡La estirada Rabiah ha abandonado la seguridad de las murallas de la ciudad!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:58
translate spanish d15a_030f19e8:

    # Na "Wow, [A]. I can't believe how long it has been."
    Na "Vaya, [A]. No puedo creer cuánto tiempo ha pasado."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:61
translate spanish d15a_56faddd4:

    # A "Yeah... I'm... also surprised."
    A "Sí... yo... también estoy sorprendida."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:64
translate spanish d15a_d99cff34:

    # "[A] looks at her cousin, somewhat taken aback, before continuing..."
    "[A] mira a su prima, algo desconcertada, antes de continuar..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:67
translate spanish d15a_cf7f304a:

    # A "You are so different from when we were younger."
    A "Eres tan diferente de cuando éramos más jóvenes."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:70
translate spanish d15a_a13e21a0:

    # Na "Yeah, I guess I have changed. I suppose uncle must have told you already that we moved back to the city not long ago."
    Na "Sí, supongo que he cambiado. Supongo que el tío ya te habrá dicho que nos mudamos a la ciudad no hace mucho."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:71
translate spanish d15a_c8909a4c:

    # Na "It's been so exciting ever since we got here!"
    Na "¡Ha sido tan emocionante desde que llegamos aquí!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:75
translate spanish d15a_bb71a9fb:

    # Na "I'm so glad I convinced mother to come here tonight."
    Na "Me alegro mucho de haber convencido a mamá para que viniera aquí esta noche."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:77
translate spanish d15a_cec33a5f:

    # "As [A] takes in the slender figure of your niece, she casually touches your crotch, pretending to lean sideways..."
    "Mientras [A] observa la esbelta figura de tu sobrina, toca casualmente tu entrepierna, fingiendo inclinarse hacia un lado..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:78
translate spanish d15a_e11387d5:

    # Na "I swear, if it wasn't for my stepdad keeping me almost a prisoner in the house, I would've come here sooner!"
    Na "Lo juro, si no fuera porque mi padrastro me mantiene casi prisionera en la casa, ¡habría venido aquí antes!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:82
translate spanish d15a_78d41c4a:

    # A "I'm happy you did, though! [persistent.mom!c] and [persistent.dad!c] have been visiting you so much, I was really feeling left out!"
    A "¡Pero estoy feliz de que lo hayas hecho! [persistent.mom!c] y [persistent.dad!c] te han estado visitando tanto que realmente me sentía excluida."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:83
translate spanish d15a_77567607:

    # Na "I know right! Uncle and I caught up a lot since. We actually get along great!"
    Na "¡Lo sé, verdad! Tío y yo nos pusimos al día mucho desde entonces. ¡De hecho, nos llevamos muy bien!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:85
translate spanish d15a_9d2761a8:

    # Na "I always looked up to him even when we were younger, but he's actually really fun too..."
    Na "Siempre le admiré, incluso cuando éramos más jóvenes, pero en realidad también es muy divertido..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:88
translate spanish d15a_f0353d34:

    # Na "But, wow. I have to say, [A]. You really have grown too since we met."
    Na "Pero, vaya. Tengo que decirlo, [A]. Realmente has crecido también desde que nos vimos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:89
translate spanish d15a_62ad75b0:

    # A "Oh, um... do you think? You're still taller, just like in the past."
    A "Oh, um... ¿Eso crees? Aún eres más alta, como en el pasado."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:92
translate spanish d15a_e15b9397:

    # Na "Yeah, I do! I mean let's be real, those boobs of yours grew so much..."
    Na "¡Sí, lo soy! Quiero decir, seamos realistas, esas tetas tuyas crecieron tanto..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:93
translate spanish d15a_15db045f:

    # A "I... guess they did."
    A "Yo... supongo que sí."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:96
translate spanish d15a_7651bf42:

    # Na "I remember that before I left to stay in the village, you were already starting to show, and I was still as flat as a pancake. But now..?!"
    Na "Recuerdo que antes de irme a vivir al pueblo, tú ya empezabas a despuntar, y yo seguía tan plana como una tortita. ¡¿Pero ahora...?!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:97
translate spanish d15a_c76efd84:

    # Na "The boys must've been all over you, in school! I'm jealous!"
    Na "¡Los chicos debían de estar detrás de ti en la escuela! ¡Estoy celosa!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:102
translate spanish d15a_bf63c4f8:

    # Na "They look amazing. I just have to see more."
    Na "Se ven increíbles. Sólo tengo que ver más."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:103
translate spanish d15a_0b9c5649:

    # Na "Do you mind if I..."
    Na "¿Te importa si yo..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:106
translate spanish d15a_d8654138:

    # A "..."
    A "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:108
translate spanish d15a_e56dcf9c:

    # Na "Wow... that just slid right off! You sure are confident wearing this, or is it how your [persistent.dad] wants you to dress?"
    Na "Guau... ¡Esto simplemente se ha deslizado! Seguro que te sientes segura llevando esto puesto, ¿o es así como tu [persistent.dad] quiere que te vistas?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:111
translate spanish d15a_58ec2768:

    # A "It's... usually him, yeah. But I like it... and [persistent.mom], too."
    A "Esto es... normalmente él, sí. Pero me gusta... Y a [persistent.mom] también."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:112
translate spanish d15a_36e6c3f7:

    # Na "Whoa, [A]...!"
    Na "¡Guau, [A]...!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:115
translate spanish d15a_f84f0c65:

    # Na "I'm such a brat. I haven't seen my cousin in years, and here I am, groping her tits..."
    Na "Soy una mocosa. Hace años que no veo a mi prima, y aquí estoy, manoseándole las tetas..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:116
translate spanish d15a_1fed6575:

    # Na "But how can I not? I mean, look at them! You just want to stuff your face in there."
    Na "¿Pero cómo no voy a hacerlo? Quiero decir, ¡míralas! Lo único que quieres es meter la cara ahí."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:119
translate spanish d15a_b373a296:

    # Na "Wowww... they're so soft! But firm at the same time!"
    Na "Guauuu... ¡son tan suaves! ¡Pero firmes al mismo tiempo!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:122
translate spanish d15a_17c2ba7b:

    # A "Nh..."
    A "Nh..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:123
translate spanish d15a_17f651d7:

    # Na "I bet they're sensitive too. If not for the inevitable back pain I would be so jealous!"
    Na "Seguro que también son sensibles. Si no fuera por el inevitable dolor de espalda, ¡estaría tan celosa!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:126
translate spanish d15a_fa2f815f:

    # "She continues to grope [A] in an odd mixture of confidence and awkwardness..."
    "Ella continúa manoseando a [A] con una extraña mezcla de confianza y torpeza..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:127
translate spanish d15a_16b7424a:

    # Na "Uncle, um... look away for a moment, okay? It's just a girl thing, I can't resist. {i}*giggles*{/i}"
    Na "Tío, um... mira a otro lado un momento, ¿vale? Es sólo cosa de chicas, no puedo resistirme. {i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:130
translate spanish d15a_ac0b9ac7:

    # Na "So... yeah... I..."
    Na "Entonces... sí... yo..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:133
translate spanish d15a_48b58ae2:

    # Na "...I will stop now. Sorry..."
    Na "... voy a dejarlo ya. Lo siento..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:138
translate spanish d15a_2bfe62ab:

    # Na "So, mom and auntie are waiting for us outside. What do you think? Shall we join them?"
    Na "Bueno, mamá y la tía nos están esperando fuera. ¿Qué os parece? ¿Nos unimos a ellas?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:140
translate spanish d15a_63abe536:

    # Na "I've already met [S] briefly, but she said she was going to change. I have even seen one of your other girls!"
    Na "Ya he visto a [S] brevemente, pero me dijo que iba a cambiar. ¡Incluso he visto a otra de tus chicas!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:142
translate spanish d15a_94f66c35:

    # Na "I've already met [S] briefly, but she said she had to get changed."
    Na "Ya he visto a [S] brevemente, pero ella dijo que tenía que cambiarse."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:145
translate spanish d15a_94dc4dad:

    # Z "Sure, let's go outside. Let's not keep them waiting."
    Z "Claro, salgamos. No las hagamos esperar."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:149
translate spanish d15a_6c5e7941:

    # Z "Alright, Nadia. That's enough, give poor [A] a break."
    Z "Está bien, Nadia. Ya es suficiente, dale un respiro a la pobre [A]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:152
translate spanish d15a_1ed39d77:

    # Na "Why's that, uncle? Are the awesome breasts of your [persistent.da] too much to bear?"
    Na "¿Por qué, tío? ¿Los impresionantes pechos de tu [persistent.da] son demasiado para soportar?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:155
translate spanish d15a_c317464d:

    # Z "Nice try, Nadia. But I decide who gets to touch my [persistent.da], and who doesn't."
    Z "Buen intento, Nadia. Pero yo decido quién toca mi [persistent.da] y quién no."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:158
translate spanish d15a_ad81d61b:

    # Z "So, what do you think, [A]. Shall we go meet your aunt?"
    Z "Entonces, ¿qué piensas, [A]?... ¿Vamos a encontrarnos con tu tía?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:161
translate spanish d15a_53c6479f:

    # A "Um... yeah, sure!"
    A "Um... ¡sí, claro!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:166
translate spanish d15a_b93c5607:

    # Z "Alright. Let's join the ladies, they must be waiting for us."
    Z "Está bien. Unámonos a las damas, deben estar esperándonos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:174
translate spanish d15a43_80c0d34b:

    # "You head to the balcony, where the others have gathered..."
    "Te diriges al balcón, donde se han reunido las demás..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:180
translate spanish d15a43_45178ba6:

    # Na "Hey guys! I'm back!"
    Na "¡Ey chicas! ¡Ya estoy de vuelta!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:183
translate spanish d15a43_b7a5c405:

    # S "And you brought the others."
    S "Y trajiste a los demás."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:184
translate spanish d15a43_6952cfae:

    # Na "I did."
    Na "Lo hice."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:187
translate spanish d15a43_f6775efc:

    # "Upon approaching the balcony, you spot Rabiah eyeing you for once not frowning, which softens her somewhat sharp features."
    "Al acercarte al balcón, ves a Rabiah mirándote por una vez sin fruncir el ceño, lo que suaviza sus rasgos algo afilados."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:188
translate spanish d15a43_3bede3c5:

    # S "So what do you think Nadia, who has changed the most, you or [A]?"
    S "Entonces, ¿qué te parece Nadia, quién ha cambiado más, tú o [A]?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:189
translate spanish d15a43_8c30b6f0:

    # Na "Gooood question!"
    Na "¡Buena pregunta!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:192
translate spanish d15a43_194695c1:

    # Ra "Hello, brother-in-law."
    Ra "Hola, cuñado."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:195
translate spanish d15a43_390f1e31:

    # Z "Look at you, leaving the house for something other than chores. Why Rabiah I am shocked! Is that a smile I saw, just now?"
    Z "Mírate, saliendo de casa para algo más que las tareas del hogar. ¡Por qué, Rabiah, estoy en shock! ¿Es una sonrisa lo que acabo de ver?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:198
translate spanish d15a43_8b704d86:

    # "You start hugging her..."
    "Empiezas a abrazarla..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:199
translate spanish d15a43_038fe73c:

    # Ra "You're not as funny as you think, you know?"
    Ra "No eres tan gracioso como crees, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:204
translate spanish d15a43_61640d14:

    # "You place your hand on her buttock, giving it a firm squeeze."
    "Colocas tu mano sobre su nalga, apretándola firmemente."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:207
translate spanish d15a43_3766c5a6:

    # Ra "{i}*sigh*{/i} [persistent.player_name], I guess you will never change."
    Ra "{i}*suspiro*{/i} [persistent.player_name], supongo que nunca cambiarás."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:208
translate spanish d15a43_dd1de5ba:

    # Ra "What do you think Omar would say if he saw this?"
    Ra "¿Qué crees que diría Omar si viera esto?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:211
translate spanish d15a43_a3ee5371:

    # Z "I don't know, you tell me. Did he suggest you coming here?"
    Z "No lo sé, dímelo tú. ¿El te sugirió que vinieras aquí?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:212
translate spanish d15a43_f1473670:

    # Ra "No, not exactly. I guess I have to admit that your words gave me something to think about."
    Ra "No, no exactamente. Supongo que debo admitir que tus palabras me dieron algo en qué pensar."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:220
translate spanish d15a43_c43d74b4:

    # Z "So, how are things in Rabiah's household?"
    Z "Entonces, ¿cómo van las cosas en la casa de Rabiah?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:221
translate spanish d15a43_c7deedbf:

    # Ra "Rabiah's household, hm? That's a joke! Last I knew, my husband owns everything inside it."
    Ra "La casa de Rabiah, ¿eh? ¡Eso es una broma! Lo último que supe es que mi marido es dueño de todo lo que hay dentro."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:222
translate spanish d15a43_0191fe19:

    # Z "You have to admit that it has a ring to it."
    Z "Tienes que admitir que suena bien."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:223
translate spanish d15a43_303a4efd:

    # Ra "You're not wrong, [persistent.player_name]."
    Ra "No te equivocas, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:229
translate spanish d15a60_d66a74e3:

    # Ra "Anyway, after your last visit, I have decided to change a few things in our lives."
    Ra "De todos modos, después de tu última visita, he decidido cambiar algunas cosas en nuestras vidas."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:230
translate spanish d15a60_2006ef1e:

    # Ra "And that included letting my daughter out of her cage."
    Ra "Y eso incluía dejar a mi hija salir de su jaula."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:233
translate spanish d15a60_016969b0:

    # Z "Well then, I am glad that your changes haven't gone so far as to let her come all this way on her own."
    Z "Bueno, entonces me alegro de que tus cambios no hayan llegado tan lejos como para permitirle llegar hasta aquí sola."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:236
translate spanish d15a60_1f9a7096:

    # Ra "Oh, I am not here just to chaperone her."
    Ra "Oh, no estoy aquí sólo para acompañarla."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:237
translate spanish d15a60_3a5f4c7b:

    # Ra "I wanted to see your [persistent.da]s again, after all these years."
    Ra "Yo quería volver a ver tus [persistent.da]s, después de todos estos años."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:240
translate spanish d15a60_8ada2721:

    # Zt "Sure you did..."
    Zt "Seguro que sí..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:243
translate spanish d15a60_cce5a0b4:

    # Ra "But don't be disheartened. I have accepted that it would be foolish to stop my daughter from having her own adventures."
    Ra "Pero no te desanimes. He aceptado que sería una tontería impedir que mi hija tenga sus propias aventuras."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:246
translate spanish d15a60_cbd5af4e:

    # "She gives you a look that you don't quite know how to interpret..."
    "Ella te lanza una mirada que no sabes muy bien interpretar..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:249
translate spanish d15a60_6c3eba25:

    # S "I can't get over your hair, Nadia. I somehow remember it being darker than it actually is, and you were keeping it so short that all these curls didn't show at all."
    S "No puedo olvidar tu cabello, Nadia. De alguna manera recuerdo que era más oscuro de lo que realmente es, y lo mantuviste tan corto que todos esos rizos no se veían en absoluto."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:252
translate spanish d15a60_263deba9:

    # "You move between them..."
    "Te mueves entre ellas..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:255
translate spanish d15a60_210622ae:

    # S "And not just that. You look so much happier and grown up than back then!"
    S "Y no sólo eso. ¡Te ves mucho más feliz y mayor que en aquel entonces!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:256
translate spanish d15a60_89f27e27:

    # S "I am really happy for you."
    S "Estoy muy feliz por ti."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:259
translate spanish d15a60_ef91cf61:

    # Na "That's... very nice, thank you."
    Na "Eso es... muy bonito, gracias."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:260
translate spanish d15a60_29e73143:

    # Na "Yeah... I was a child when we left the city, and you were already starting your training. I guess you never really saw me."
    Na "Sí... Yo era una niña cuando nos fuimos de la ciudad, y tú ya estabas empezando tu entrenamiento. Supongo que nunca llegaste a verme."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:261
translate spanish d15a60_23cd2162:

    # Na "Not that I blame you. I know I have done some growing up, in the last few years."
    Na "No es que te culpe. Sé que he madurado bastante en los últimos años."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:264
translate spanish d15a60_45c62c15:

    # S "I've heard about it..."
    S "He oído hablar de eso..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:267
translate spanish d15a60_bcfde816:

    # "As the family reunion proceeds, you notice open admiration in [A]'s expression towards her cousin."
    "A medida que avanza la reunión familiar, se nota una abierta admiración en la expresión de [A] hacia su prima."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:268
translate spanish d15a60_9a84500d:

    # "You wonder if [A] might be comparing herself to her cousin, who seems to carry herself in a much more confident and mature way, despite being pretty much of the same age."
    "Uno se pregunta si [A] podría estar comparándose con su prima, quien parece comportarse de una manera mucho más segura y madura, a pesar de tener más o menos la misma edad."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:269
translate spanish d15a60_643db817:

    # "You make a mental note to keep an eye on [A] in the coming days."
    "Haces una nota mental para estar pendiente de [A] en los próximos días."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:273
translate spanish d15a60_fbc11743:

    # "You all enjoy a few drinks and some banter together, reminishing about years past, as the evening approaches and old familial bonds are renewed."
    "Disfrutáis todos juntos de unas copas y algunas bromas, recordando años pasados, mientras se acerca la noche y se renuevan viejos lazos familiares."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:274
translate spanish d15a60_d1c85fcb:

    # "Eventually, Rabiah announces that it is time for them to return to the city."
    "Finalmente, Rabiah anuncia que es hora de que regresen a la ciudad."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:280
translate spanish re_d15a73_38e1f0bd:

    # Na "So uhm... I need to visit the bathroom."
    Na "Bueno uhm... tengo que ir al baño."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:281
translate spanish re_d15a73_e4f240d5:

    # Na "Can anyone show me the way?"
