# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1115
translate spanish d15a219_1e512692:

    # "A while later..."
    "Pasado un rato..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1118
translate spanish d15a219_76077b89:

    # Ra "It was so nice to see how much you have grown, [S]."
    Ra "Ha sido muy satisfactorio ver lo mucho que has crecido, [S]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1119
translate spanish d15a219_df851b74:

    # Ra "And I don't just mean physically, I mean as a woman, too. I always liked you a lot, you know."
    Ra "Y no me refiero sólo físicamente, también me refiero como mujer. Siempre me gustaste mucho, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1122
translate spanish d15a219_be0cf5bd:

    # Ra "It's good to see that after all these years, you haven't become a copy of your mother, but became your own person with your own ambitions."
    Ra "Es bueno ver que después de todos estos años, no te has convertido en una copia de tu madre, sino que te has convertido en tu propia persona con tus propias ambiciones."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1123
translate spanish d15a219_a4d1756f:

    # Ra "I guess your [persistent.dad] is a good teacher, after all."
    Ra "Supongo que tu [persistent.dad] es un buen maestro, después de todo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1126
translate spanish d15a219_211d407d:

    # S "Thank you very much, aunt Rabiah! I have missed you, you know? You were always nice to us children."
    S "¡Muchas gracias, tía Rabiah! Te he echado de menos, ¿sabes? Siempre fuiste amable con nosotras, las niñas."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1129
translate spanish d15a219_0af75625:

    # S "We should meet again soon. There are still stories that I want you to tell us."
    S "Deberíamos volver a vernos pronto. Aún hay historias que quiero que nos cuentes."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1132
translate spanish d15a219_460f9769:

    # Ra "Well, I am sure that that can be arranged. I am feeling more outgoing lately."
    Ra "Bueno, estoy segura de que eso se puede arreglar. Últimamente me siento más extrovertida."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1135
translate spanish d15a219_ff3c76ce:

    # Ra "Alright then, where is {i}my{/i} daughter, though?"
    Ra "Muy bien, entonces, ¿dónde está {i}mi{/i} hija?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1136
translate spanish d15a219_97b2bda7:

    # Ra "{i}*sigh*{/i} She always does keep me waiting for her."
    Ra "{i}*suspiro*{/i} Siempre me hace esperar por ella."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1139
translate spanish d15a219_c2c9cc07:

    # W "..."
    W "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1143
translate spanish d15a219_9d2f10f8:

    # Z "Ladies, I have found our two missing girls."
    Z "Señoras, he encontrado a nuestras dos pequeñas desaparecidas."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1145
translate spanish d15a219_02abcdc2:

    # Z "I guess we have to wait a little longer."
    Z "Supongo que tendremos que esperar un poco más."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1149
translate spanish d15a219_02dbe69f:

    # Ww "How did it go, husband?"
    Ww "¿Cómo te fue, marido?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1150
translate spanish d15a219_e2f12d8f:

    # Zw "Pretty much as you might expect."
    Zw "Más o menos como cabría de esperar."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1153
translate spanish d15a219_1db0bb3e:

    # Zw "Although... I've had to keep them both in line at the same time."
    Zw "Aunque... he tenido que mantenerlas a ambas a raya al mismo tiempo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1156
translate spanish d15a219_177151c3:

    # Ww "Let me guess, [A] just couldn't stand by while you two were at it?"
    Ww "Déjame adivinar, ¿[A] no podía quedarse de brazos cruzados mientras vosotros dos lo hacíais?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1159
translate spanish d15a219_5c95136f:

    # Zw "It's so easy for her to feel left out. She can be jealous too, to my surprise."
    Zw "Es muy fácil para ella sentirse excluida. Para mi sorpresa, también puede ser celosa."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1163
translate spanish d15a219_98c959b9:

    # Zw "So, what do you think, should we do this again some time?"
    Zw "Entonces, ¿qué piensas? ¿Deberíamos hacer esto de nuevo en algún momento?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1164
translate spanish d15a219_574ce360:

    # Ww "I don't see why not. My sister seems a lot happier when she is not with her husband."
    Ww "No veo por qué no. Mi hermana parece mucho más feliz cuando no está con su marido."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1167
translate spanish d15a219_bf50bbb7:

    # Ww "Unlike me, of course. Especially when you hold me like that."
    Ww "A diferencia de mí, por supuesto. Especialmente cuando me abrazas así."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1170
translate spanish d15a219_cc934ff3:

    # Zw "How could I ever not?"
    Zw "¿Cómo podría no hacerlo?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1177
translate spanish d15a231_66f4ec3d:

    # Na "Hey guys, uhm... we are here now!"
    Na "Ey chicos, uhm... ¡ya estamos aquí!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1180
translate spanish d15a231_467ac3e4:

    # Na "I... I was getting lost in those rooms. It's actually quite a big place."
    Na "Yo... me estaba perdiendo en esas habitaciones. En realidad, es un lugar bastante grande."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1183
translate spanish d15a231_f0fdedc3:

    # Na "Are we going already? Okay... goodbye auntie!"
    Na "¿Ya nos vamos? Está bien... ¡Adiós tía!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1184
translate spanish d15a231_d8654138:

    # A "..."
    A "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1186
translate spanish d15a231_6f7bd742:

    # Na "Sorry! We were chatting and lost track of time!"
    Na "¡Lo siento! ¡Estábamos charlando y perdimos la noción del tiempo!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1190
translate spanish d15a231_23059474:

    # W "I hope you enjoyed your stay as much as we did."
    W "Espero que hayas disfrutado de tu estancia tanto como nosotros."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1191
translate spanish d15a231_d3cb545a:

    # Na "Oh, of course. {i}*giggle*{/i}"
    Na "Oh, por supuesto. {i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1193
translate spanish d15a231_38fffeea:

    # W "Do you feel well? You look like you've been running in the sun for hours!"
    W "¿Te sientes bien? ¡Parece que llevas horas corriendo bajo el sol!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1194
translate spanish d15a231_9f96aef2:

    # W "You might want to drink another glass of water..."
    W "Quizás quieras beber otro vaso de agua..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1197
translate spanish d15a231_cbc05da6:

    # S "Whatever you did to her, [persistent.dad], I know that she will be coming to visit again soon."
    S "Hicieras lo que hicieras con ella, [persistent.dad], lo sé..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1200
translate spanish d15a231_2f1e4f06:

    # Z "I see that you've learned to pay attention to the details, [S]. I'm proud of you."
    Z "Veo que has aprendido a prestar atención a los detalles, [S]. Estoy orgulloso de ti."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1201
translate spanish d15a231_33d127c4:

    # S "You're still a pig, [persistent.dad]!"
    S "¡Sigues siendo un cerdo, [persistent.dad]!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1202
translate spanish d15a231_07bef54d:

    # "You slap her butt, stifling a laugh."
    "Le das un azote en el culo, conteniendo una carcajada."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1204
translate spanish d15a231_c1e6eac5:

    # W "Look at you, such a grown woman. And so confident..."
    W "Mírate, toda una mujer. Y tan segura de ti misma..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1207
translate spanish d15a231_1daa279a:

    # S "She really has grown up since we last saw her, hasn't she?"
    S "Ella realmente ha crecido desde la última vez que la vimos, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1210
translate spanish d15a231_2dc0b92f:

    # Z "Absolutely. She's open for everything. I like that in her."
    Z "Absolutamente. Está abierta a todo. Eso es lo que me gusta de ella."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1213
translate spanish d15a231_53dd049e:

    # Ra "[A], my little mouse. You have seemingly grown in everything but your height."
    Ra "[A], mi ratoncito. Aparentemente has crecido en todo menos en tu altura."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1214
translate spanish d15a231_2b14a197:

    # Ra "We haven't had an opportunity to chat, but we will make up for that soon, will we?"
    Ra "No hemos tenido ocasión de charlar, pero lo compensaremos pronto, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1217
translate spanish d15a231_362f3fa5:

    # A "Sure, aunt Rabiah!"
    A "¡Claro, tía Rabiah!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1225
translate spanish d15a231_d8ca4889:

    # Ra "Make sure to listen to your [persistent.dad] and eat your vitamins, alright? You look quite weak right now."
    Ra "Asegúrate de escuchar a tu [persistent.dad] y comer tus vitaminas, ¿de acuerdo? Te ves bastante débil en este momento."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1226
translate spanish d15a231_f8bd91ac:

    # Ra "Actually... maybe that is exactly {i}because{/i} you listen to your [persistent.dad]..."
    Ra "En realidad... tal vez eso sea exactamente {i}porque{/i} escuchas a tu [persistent.dad]..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1229
translate spanish d15a231_89d799b0:

    # Ra "And also... your dress is quite disheveled..."
    Ra "Y además... tu vestido está bastante desaliñado..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1230
translate spanish d15a231_1d495b63:

    # Ra "It only takes a few seconds, to look well put together, [A]."
    Ra "Sólo se necesitan unos segundos para parecer bien arreglada, [A]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1231
translate spanish d15a231_90863b8a:

    # Ra "Oh, forget it! I am trying to change, am I not?"
    Ra "¡Oh, olvídalo! Estoy tratando de cambiar, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1237
translate spanish d15a241_e004899b:

    # Na "Thank you for the drinks, aunt [W]."
    Na "Gracias por las bebidas, tía [W]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1239
translate spanish d15a241_62eff969:

    # Na "I really enjoyed our time here. Can I have a quick goodbye kiss?"
    Na "Realmente he disfrutado mucho de nuestro tiempo aquí. ¿Me das un beso rápido de despedida?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1244
translate spanish d15a241_73790b4c:

    # W "Oh, sure, why not?"
    W "Oh, claro, ¿por qué no?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1249
translate spanish d15a241_5c837578:

    # Na "{i}*kissing*{/i}"
    Na "{i}*beso*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1252
translate spanish d15a241_95ac65d5:

    # "You watch as Nadia takes her time to give your wife a good and long kiss on the lips..."
    "Ves como Nadia se toma su tiempo para darle un buen y largo beso en los labios a tu mujer..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1255
translate spanish d15a241_2a66a78c:

    # W "Nadia...? You're so eager today..."
    W "¿Nadia...? Hoy estás muy ansiosa..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1258
translate spanish d15a241_87921721:

    # W "...?"
    W "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1261
translate spanish d15a241_33a8eca8:

    # Na "..."
    Na "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1262
translate spanish d15a241_49ae92c0:

    # W "Ngh..."
    W "Ngh..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1265
translate spanish d15a241_5bbb73e4:

    # Na "Nlhh..."
    Na "Nlhh..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1268
translate spanish d15a241_779e843b:

    # Zt "Is that... what I think it is...?"
    Zt "¿Es eso... lo que creo que es...?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1271
translate spanish d15a241_80a9f83c:

    # Na "Thank you again, auntie. I hope you will visit us again soon!"
    Na "Gracias de nuevo, tía. ¡Espero que vuelvas a visitarnos pronto!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1272
translate spanish d15a241_c5ea7830:

    # Na "Uncle [persistent.player_name] also enjoyed today a lot..."
    Na "También el tío [persistent.player_name] lo disfrutó mucho hoy..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1275
translate spanish d15a241_d33e084f:

    # Na "Bye bye, guys! Mom, let's go?"
    Na "¡Adiós chicas! Mamá, ¿nos vamos?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1278
translate spanish d15a241_cfc30c2e:

    # W "{i}*gulp*{/i}"
    W "{i}*gulp*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1280
translate spanish d15a241_1532486c:

    # Na "I hope you will come to visit us again, soon?"
    Na "Espero que vuelvas a visitarnos pronto."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1285
translate spanish d15a241_a72f98eb:

    # W "I am pretty sure your uncle won't have anything against it."
    W "Estoy bastante segura de que tu tío no tendrá nada en contra."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1286
translate spanish d15a241_8b79762d:

    # W "Until then, don't get into too much trouble out there, alright?"
    W "Hasta entonces, no te metas en muchos problemas, ¿de acuerdo?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1289
translate spanish d15a241_47d610a8:

    # Na "Me? Of course not..."
    Na "¿Yo? Por supuesto que no..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1290
translate spanish d15a241_428b63a9:

    # Na "Bye bye, auntie!"
    Na "¡Adiós, tía!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1310
translate spanish d15b_1ef9888d:

    # S "Hey..."
    S "Ey..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1313
translate spanish d15b_50512010:

    # Z "Hey, [S]."
    Z "Hola, [S]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1316
translate spanish d15b_fe3f6f19:

    # S "Enjoying the sunset?"
    S "¿Disfrutando del atardecer?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1319
translate spanish d15b_e89c29d7:

    # Z "I am. Trying to relax a bit, after all that's happened recently."
    Z "Así es. Intento relajarme un poco, después de todo lo que ha pasado últimamente."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1320
translate spanish d15b_f49b417a:

    # Z "What about you? Have you slept well since then?"
    Z "¿Y tú? ¿Has dormido bien desde entonces?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1323
translate spanish d15b_f85c7657:

    # S "It could be worse. I'm home and safe. I have had a few scares in the first nights, but that's mostly gone now."
    S "Podría ser peor. Estoy en casa y a salvo. Tuve algunos sustos las primeras noches, pero ya casi todo eso ha desaparecido."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1326
translate spanish d15b_96c4161c:

    # Z "That's good to hear."
    Z "Me alegro de oírlo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1327
translate spanish d15b_658a8a34:

    # Z "You look amazing in this dress."
    Z "Te ves increíble con ese vestido."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1330
translate spanish d15b_eee488ce:

    # S "Thanks, I am glad you like it."
    S "Gracias, me alegra de que te guste."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1334
translate spanish d15b_7b806097:

    # S "I have been thinking about the future."
    S "He estado pensando en el futuro."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1337
translate spanish d15b_16a3d0a3:

    # Z "Do you want to discuss about it?"
    Z "¿Quieres hablar de ello?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1340
translate spanish d15b_fca02548:

    # S "Well, I am a Stalker now, I figure I should find a way to put my name out there, for people to know me, and find some commissions, make some contacts."
    S "Bueno, ahora soy una Acechadora, creo que debería encontrar una manera de dar a conocer mi nombre, para que la gente me conozca, encontrar algunas comisiones y hacer algunos contactos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1343
translate spanish d15b_682f4dd2:

    # Z "You know that you won't lack for opportunities, right? You already have a foot in the door at the palace. That's more than the average Stalker can count on."
    Z "Sabes que no te faltarán oportunidades, ¿verdad? Ya tienes un pie en la puerta del palacio. Eso es más de lo que el Acechador promedio puede contar."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1346
translate spanish d15b_245cdd97:

    # S "That's true, but I figured that that was mostly your thing. The Queen relies on you."
    S "Es cierto, pero supuse que eso era sobre todo cosa tuya. La Reina confía en ti."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1349
translate spanish d15b_c47fe598:

    # Z "And on you by proxy. She showed interest in your expedition and gave you a task, not me."
    Z "Y en ti por poder. Ella mostró interés por tu expedición y te encomendó una tarea, no yo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1352
translate spanish d15b_4bb8512a:

    # S "Mmh, I agree. But I do want to also find my own way, not just rely on you for everything."
    S "Mmh, estoy de acuerdo. Pero también quiero encontrar mi propio camino, no sólo depender de ti para todo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1355
translate spanish d15b_9470472a:

    # Z "That goes to your credit. There's no shame in using the tools you're given though. I am sure Igor won't deny you a few good leads, if he should stumble on them."
    Z "Eso es tu mérito. Sin embargo, no es ninguna vergüenza usar las herramientas que te dan. Estoy seguro de que Igor no te negará algunas buenas pistas, si se topa con ellas."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1356
translate spanish d15b_5a1a3ae2:

    # Z "He dotes on you as much as he is a friend of mine."
    Z "Te adora tanto como si fuera amigo mío."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1359
translate spanish d15b_a02a8022:

    # S "Maybe I'll have a talk with him. See if he can also point me to a few new suppliers."
    S "Tal vez hable con él. A ver si también puede indicarme algunos proveedores nuevos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1366
translate spanish d15b_2774bf23:

    # "You talk shop with [S], relaxing on the balcony, and sketching out a few potential expeditions that you might undertake in the future."
    "Hablas de negocios con [S], te relajas en el balcón y esbozas algunas expediciones potenciales que podrías emprender en el futuro."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1367
translate spanish d15b_8403a6ac:

    # "Eventually, you both decide to call it a night."
    "Al final, ambos decidís dar por terminada la noche."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1372
translate spanish d15b_5521e935:

    # S "So... um..."
    S "Entonces... um..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1373
translate spanish d15b_5793514b:

    # S "I have been thinking about our time at the oasis..."
    S "He estado pensando en nuestro tiempo en el oasis..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1376
translate spanish d15b_2fb4caff:

    # S "It was something I thought about for a long time but...where do we go from there?"
    S "Fue algo en lo que pensé durante mucho tiempo, pero... ¿dónde vamos a partir de ahí?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1379
translate spanish d15b_4b8656f0:

    # S "You know...since we've done it, what now?"
    S "Sabes... ya que lo hemos hecho, ¿ahora qué?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1382
translate spanish d15b_fbb1bb2d:

    # S "I have been to the Zone; I have survived the challenge. You said I am a Stalker now."
    S "He estado en la Zona; he sobrevivido al desafío. Dijiste que ahora soy una Acechadora."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1385
translate spanish d15b_a87c1b60:

    # Z "It is true that the years that led up to this are now over. You are not a trainee anymore."
    Z "Es cierto que los años que condujeron a esto ya pasaron. Ya no eres un aprendiz."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1388
translate spanish d15b_a8f124cc:

    # S "So... there is no longer a reason to be reserved, is there?"
    S "Entonces... ya no hay razón para ser reservada, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1391
translate spanish d15b_b6b03cfc:

    # S "But I still...wonder if this causes you to think of me more like [A]?"
    S "Pero todavía... me pregunto si esto hace que pienses en mí más como en ¿[A]?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1394
translate spanish d15b_80cd66f0:

    # Z "You and your sister were always different, and what we did will not change that."
    Z "Tú y tu hermana siempre fuisteis diferentes, y lo que hicimos no cambiará eso."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1397
translate spanish d15b_f34f9430:

    # Z "You know where your passions lie. Us enjoying each other should have no impact on it."
    Z "Sabes dónde residen tus pasiones. El hecho de que disfrutemos el uno del otro no debería tener ningún impacto en ello."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1400
translate spanish d15b_ab4999f4:

    # S "Thank you [persistent.dad]. That's good to hear and yes, I want to see what else is out there, see what life has to offer."
    S "Gracias [persistent.dad]. Es bueno oir eso y sí, quiero ver qué más hay por ahí, ver qué tiene la vida para ofrecer."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1401
translate spanish d15b_fccd6e08:

    # S "Put my skills to good use, you know?"
    S "Hacer un buen uso de mis habilidades, ¿sabes?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1404
translate spanish d15b_f4b7b797:

    # Z "And I will be there to assist if you want me to."
    Z "Y yo estaré allí para ayudarte si así lo deseas."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1406
translate spanish d15b_135afd97:

    # Z "You will always be my [persistent.da], no matter how old you grow."
    Z "Siempre serás mi [persistent.da], sin importar la edad que tengas."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1409
translate spanish d15b_12368a77:

    # S "But...exploring tombs and going on missions is not all I want to do together with you."
    S "Pero... explorar tumbas y realizar misiones no es todo lo que quiero hacer junto a ti."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1412
translate spanish d15b_b8617839:

    # S "Other than messing around a bit with [A], I have mostly put that part of me in a corner while I was focusing on my training."
    S "Aparte de jugar un poco con [A], mayormente he arrinconado esa parte de mí mientras me concentraba en mi entrenamiento."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1415
translate spanish d15b_2fda71a0:

    # S "Since I have put this behind me now...I think I deserve to have a little fun, so...will you teach me?"
    S "Ya que dejé esto atrás... creo que merezco divertirme un poco, así que... ¿me enseñarás?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:1418
translate spanish d15b_87060630:

    # Z "If you want me to, I think I can find a thing or two to teach you still."
