translate spanish ss43_c45c2c84:

    # "She keeps stroking you while focusing her efforts on your tip."
    "Sigue acariciándote mientras concentra sus esfuerzos en tu punta."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2090
translate spanish ss43_26ae378d:

    # Zt "She is... so good for her first time."
    Zt "Ella es... muy buena para su primera vez."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2092
translate spanish ss43_4930b990:

    # Zt "A natural talent... like her mother."
    Zt "Un talento natural... como su madre."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2094
translate spanish ss43_a711aa67:

    # Zt "A natural talent... like [W]."
    Zt "Un talento natural... como [W]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2095
translate spanish ss43_1799fd44:

    # S "{i}*slurp*{/i}"
    S "{i}*chupa*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2097
translate spanish ss43_4bd3b6d6:

    # Z "You're... wow."
    Z "Eres... guau."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2098
translate spanish ss43_03dab914:

    # Z "A multitasking talent."
    Z "Un talento multitarea."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2099
translate spanish ss43_3102cb04:

    # S "Mhm... {i}*muffled giggling*{/i}"
    S "Mhm... {i}*risitas amoriguadas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2101
translate spanish ss43_71fbb520:

    # "She keeps her focus up, trying her best to go as deep as she can."
    "Ella mantiene su enfoque, haciendo lo posible por ir tan profundo como puede."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2102
translate spanish ss43_1063197a:

    # Z "You're making me pass out, [S]."
    Z "Me estás haciendo desmayarme, [S]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2103
translate spanish ss43_d692fc59_1:

    # S "{i}*sucking*{/i}"
    S "{i}*chupando*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2105
translate spanish ss43_6d97e2c5:

    # Z "A little bit more..."
    Z "Un poco más..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2107
translate spanish ss43_3782cf63:

    # Z "[S]... careful. I'm..."
    Z "[S]... con cuidado. Estoy..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2108
translate spanish ss43_1308e93f:

    # Z "Ah... this is too much..-"
    Z "Ah... esto es demasiado..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2114
translate spanish ss43_e156dcdd:

    # Z "Ngh-"
    Z "Ngh..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2120
translate spanish ss43_d120afb7:

    # Z "[S], wait... what are you-"
    Z "[S], espera... ¿qué estás-"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2126
translate spanish ss43_8e100d1a:

    # Z "Agh-"
    Z "Agh-"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2129
translate spanish ss43_971a98df_1:

    # S "..."
    S "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2135
translate spanish ss43_d50513a1:

    # Z "I... {i}*pant*{/i}"
    Z "Yo... {i}*jadeo*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2136
translate spanish ss43_cba70028:

    # Z "Did you just..."
    Z "¿Acabas de..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2139
translate spanish ss43_876fc97f:

    # S "I wanthed to... thaste it."
    S "Yo quería... probarlo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2142
translate spanish ss43_36160084:

    # S "{i}*gulp*{/i}"
    S "{i}*traga*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2145
translate spanish ss43_5a5e0cd1:

    # S "A girl has to try new things... {i}*giggles*{/i}"
    S "Una chica tiene que probar cosas nuevas... {i}*risitas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2148
translate spanish ss43_3d7d0557:

    # Z "She has to, indeed."
    Z "en efecto, tiene que hacerlo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2153
translate spanish ss43_97ed0aeb:

    # "She cleans herself and climbs back alongside you..."
    "Ella se limpia y vuelve a subir junto a ti..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2156
translate spanish ss43_0837e8aa:

    # S "That was nice, wasn't it?"
    S "Ha estado genial, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2157
translate spanish ss43_67f8ca47:

    # Z "Absolutely."
    Z "Por supuesto."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2160
translate spanish ss43_07d722ed:

    # S "So... I guess we're doing these things more often from now on?"
    S "Entonces... ¿supongo que haremos estas cosas con más frecuencia a partir de ahora?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2163
translate spanish ss43_908e8e34:

    # Z "I could stand to do this more often, yes."
    Z "Podría soportar hacer esto más a menudo, sí."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2166
translate spanish ss43_6f774b0c:

    # S "And that means... we could sleep together in the evening sometimes, as well."
    S "Y eso significa... que a veces también podríamos dormir juntos por la noche."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2169
translate spanish ss43_3211e048:

    # Z "Do you want me to stay, tonight? We've already told your [persistent.mom]."
    Z "¿Quieres que me quede esta noche? Ya se lo hemos dicho a tu [persistent.mom]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2172
translate spanish ss43_c0c6457f:

    # S "I would like that."
    S "Eso me gustaría."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2181
translate spanish ss43_6249949a:

    # "You cuddle in the warm candlelight, quickly getting sleepy after such an intense evening."
    "Te acurrucas a la cálida luz de las velas y rápidamente te entra el sueño después de una velada tan intensa."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2182
translate spanish ss43_a388b022:

    # "You feel that the relationship with your [persistent.da] has reached another level tonight."
    "Sientes que la relación con tu [persistent.da] ha alcanzado otro nivel esta noche."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2183
translate spanish ss43_cf1c5173:

    # "While you are still feeling things out, you are both more open about each other's sexual desires."
    "Mientras aún estáis tanteando el terreno, ambos sois más abiertos sobre los deseos sexuales del otro."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2186
translate spanish ss43_693413e8:

    # "Your future adventures together will surely be exciting..."
    "Vuestras futuras aventuras juntos seguro que serán emocionantes..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2199
translate spanish d15c_85c31f43:

    # "You head directly towards [I]'s hideout."
    "Te diriges directamente hacia el escondite de [I]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2200
translate spanish d15c_65555694:

    # "Hours later..."
    "Horas más tarde..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2210
translate spanish d15c_c8649ed6:

    # Z "[I]?"
    Z "¿[I]?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2213
translate spanish d15c_ba1cf760:

    # Z "I'm back."
    Z "He vuelto."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2216
translate spanish d15c_68da0ba3:

    # "She turns around facing you as you stand in front of her..."
    "Se da vuelta hacia ti mientras te paras frente a ella..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2219
translate spanish d15c_95cf3aed:

    # Z "I hope this isn't the wrong time, and that your friend has returned."
    Z "Espero que no sea un mal momento y que tu amiga haya regresado."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2220
translate spanish d15c_47b654a0:

    # Z "I'm not quite sure how I can help, but... well, I'm here."
    Z "No estoy muy seguro de cómo puedo ayudar, pero... Bueno, estoy aquí."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2223
translate spanish d15c_1df8a34b:

    # "She stands up..."
    "Ella se levanta..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2226
translate spanish d15c_848cb1ab:

    # I "Thank you for coming back."
    I "Gracias por volver."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2227
translate spanish d15c_c22c84cb:

    # I "She was here yesterday."
    I "Ella estuvo aquí ayer."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2230
translate spanish d15c_1bd2c54e:

    # I "Unfortunately... she didn't stay very long."
    I "Desafortunadamente... no se quedó mucho tiempo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2231
translate spanish d15c_a48be620:

    # I "I wish she would stay here, where it's safe, but I can't force her."
    I "Ojalá se quedara aquí, donde es seguro, pero no puedo obligarla."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2234
translate spanish d15c_8416bbc3:

    # I "But... if you stay around for a while, she might come back."
    I "Pero... si te quedas aquí por un tiempo, ella podría regresar."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2237
translate spanish d15c_4f5abb60:

    # Z "Sure, I can use a short rest, before I drive back again."
    Z "Claro, me vendría bien un breve descanso antes de volver a conducir."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2240
translate spanish d15c_c19ac202:

    # "She smiles..."
    "Ella sonríe..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2241
translate spanish d15c_b4dcbee3:

    # Z "So... what is it exactly you do around here? I understand the luxury of having all this water, but I'm sure you don't spend all day bathing, right?"
    Z "Entonces... ¿qué es exactamente lo que haces por aquí? Entiendo el lujo de tener toda esta agua, pero estoy seguro de que no te pasas todo el día bañándote, ¿verdad?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2244
translate spanish d15c_320868d8:

    # I "There is always something to do here. Let me show you."
    I "Aquí siempre hay algo que hacer. Deja que te lo enseñe."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2247
translate spanish d15c_d99fb79e:

    # Z "Lead the way."
    Z "Tú primero."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2250
translate spanish d15c_d194d975:

    # "She jumps off the platform she was standing on, walking past you..."
    "Ella salta de la plataforma en la que estaba parada y pasa junto a ti..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2253
translate spanish d15c_4241f19a:

    # I "I have something in mind that you will find interesting."
    I "Tengo algo en mente que te resultará interesante."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2258
translate spanish d15c_14f4574d:

    # "She leads you to a different section of the enclosure..."
    "Ella te lleva a una sección diferente del recinto..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2264
translate spanish d15c_5018f220:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2265
translate spanish d15c_25b3f44c:

    # Z "This... this is new."
    Z "Esto... esto es nuevo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2268
translate spanish d15c_449d3db6:

    # "As you stand at the entrance of a sparsely illuminated cave, you observe that a fine blue mist rises from the ground concealing something."
    "Cuando estás a la entrada de una cueva escasamente iluminada, observas que una fina niebla azul se eleva desde el suelo y oculta algo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2269
translate spanish d15c_5d217ca0:

    # "When your eyes adjust, you notice a thick carpet of the same blue-ish grass that you have seen in [I]'s cave before."
    "Cuando tus ojos se adaptan, notas una gruesa alfombra de la misma hierba azulada que has visto antes en la cueva de [I]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2270
translate spanish d15c_0437ee04:

    # "As the blue mist shifts and weaves in the soft wind that flows from the entrance of the cave, you notice strands of blue, turquoise and green petals, sprouting from long reeds that emerge bobbing in the mist."
    "A medida que la niebla azul cambia y se teje con el suave viento que fluye desde la entrada de la cueva, notas hebras de pétalos azules, turquesas y verdes que brotan de largos juncos que emergen balanceándose en la niebla."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2271
translate spanish d15c_b6f6834d:

    # "Using what little light you get from a spotlight at the back of this cave, you look at the flowers without recognising them."
    "Con la poca luz que te llega de un foco en el fondo de esta cueva, miras las flores sin reconocerlas."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2274
translate spanish d15c_254b09f4:

    # "You follow [I] as she kneels down in the mist..."
    "Sigues a [I] mientras ella se arrodilla en la niebla..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2277
translate spanish d15c_2b5f6b5a:

    # Z "These look very pretty. I have never seen anything quite like it. Are they this colour because of the mist, or are the plants what gives colour to the mist?"
    Z "Se ven muy bonitas. Nunca había visto nada parecido. ¿Son de este color debido a la niebla, o son las plantas las que le dan color a la niebla?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2280
translate spanish d15c_03d904cb:

    # I "I am not certain how that particular cycle started. They were growing here before Sonmi and I even discovered this place."
    I "No estoy segura de cómo comenzó ese ciclo en particular. Estaban creciendo aquí antes de que Sonmi y yo descubriéramos este lugar."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2281
translate spanish d15c_9f7703f7:

    # I "We discovered that their flowers can be consumed. And so, we grew and carefully cultivated them over the years."
    I "Descubrimos que sus flores se pueden consumir. Y así, las cultivamos cuidadosamente a lo largo de los años."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2284
translate spanish d15c_f1817070:

    # I "Do you want to come closer?"
    I "¿Quieres acercarte?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2287
translate spanish d15c_d980726e:

    # Z "I think I have seen something similar in the past, but only in the Zone, and never this bright and colourful."
    Z "Creo que he visto algo similar en el pasado, pero sólo en la Zona, y nunca tan brillante y colorido."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2288
translate spanish d15c_cedf9484:

    # Z "I assume they only grow here?"
    Z "¿Supongo que sólo crecen aquí?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2291
translate spanish d15c_bc8297dc:

    # I "Most likely, I haven't seen them anywhere else. I think that the combination of humidity, shadow and airflow is just the right habitat for these beauties."
    I "Lo más probable es que no las haya visto en ningún otro lugar. Creo que la combinación de humedad, sombra y corriente de aire es el hábitat adecuado para estas bellezas."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2292
translate spanish d15c_a92254d5:

    # I "They grow quickly, and they are more nutritious than any other fruit."
    I "Crecen rápidamente y son más nutritivas que cualquier otra fruta."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2295
translate spanish d15c_f2c56974:

    # I "Over time, I have come to the conclusion that the flowers somehow seem to participate in the production of this mist, much like other plants help create the air we breathe."
    I "Con el tiempo, he llegado a la conclusión de que las flores parecen participar de alguna manera en la producción de esta niebla, al igual que otras plantas ayudan a crear el aire que respiramos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2298
translate spanish d15c_ea0941cf:

    # I "From what Sonmi tells me there's a high concentration of oxygen, and possibly some other chemicals we can't quite identify."
    I "Por lo que me dice Sonmi, hay una alta concentración de oxígeno y posiblemente algunas otras sustancias químicas que no podemos identificar del todo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2301
translate spanish d15c_a31616fa:

    # "You consider yourself a learned man, but your experience with plants and biology in general is broadly limited to what [W] prepares for you. You keep listening, captivated."
    "Te consideras un hombre culto, pero tu experiencia con las plantas y la biología en general se limita en gran medida a lo que [W] prepara para ti. Sigues escuchando, cautivado."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2304
translate spanish d15c_68dcd160:

    # I "You can try them, if you want?"
    I "¿Puedes probarlas, si quieres?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2307
translate spanish d15c_1217d2c9:

    # Z "Hm. Sure, I could use a bite."
    Z "Hm. Claro, me vendría bien un bocado."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2310
translate spanish d15c_3ef5620f:

    # Z "Let's see.. this one looks good. They feel quite firm."
    Z "Veamos... este se ve bien. Se sienten bastante firmes."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2313
translate spanish d15c_90a80689:

    # Z "{i}*bites*{/i} Hm..."
    Z "{i}*mordisco*{/i} Hm..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2316
translate spanish d15c_a47e4ff3:

    # Z "{i}*chews*{/i}"
    Z "{i}*masticar*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2317
translate spanish d15c_5018f220_1:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2318
translate spanish d15c_6b39df18:

    # extend " ...."
    extend " ...."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2319
translate spanish d15c_647e4462:

    # extend " ....."
    extend " ....."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2322
translate spanish d15c_1944164b:

    # Z "{i}*cough*{/i} Fuck..."
    Z "{i}*tos*{/i} Joder..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2323
translate spanish d15c_5e6a404e:

    # "You spit out a mouthful..."
    "Escupes un bocado..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2324
translate spanish d15c_f1def5c7:

    # Z "That... oh gods..."
    Z "Esto... oh dioses..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2325
translate spanish d15c_2ca71be3:

    # I "Mhhh..."
    I "Mhhh..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2328
translate spanish d15c_81bc0e66:

    # I "{i}*giggles* Oh no..."
    I "{i}*risitas* Oh no..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2331
translate spanish d15c_d2eba430:

    # I "I didn't mean you should eat it raw. You ate the whole thing, just like that! {i}*laughing*{/i}"
    I "No quise decir que te lo comieras cruda. ¡Te la comiste entera, así! {i}*risas*{/i}"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2334
translate spanish d15c_02ae2c8c:

    # Z "Very funny! I have to admit, I didn't think this through."
    Z "¡Muy graciosa! Tengo que admitir que no lo pensé bien."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2337
translate spanish d15c_5e2b0a80:

    # Z "So, what do you want me to do? Collect the most colourful flowers?"
    Z "Entonces, ¿qué quieres que haga? ¿Coleccionar las flores más coloridas?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2338
translate spanish d15c_ddc9a42f:

    # I "Yes, if you would. We can take these two bags and each take a side of the cave."
    I "Sí, si quieres. Podemos agarrar estas dos bolsas y recorrer cada uno un lado de la cueva."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2339
translate spanish d15c_89c3c779:

    # Z "I see."
    Z "Ya veo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2342
translate spanish d15c_f8be7967:

    # Z "You... really have everything you need right here, don't you?"
    Z "Tú... realmente tienes todo lo que necesitas aquí, ¿no?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2343
translate spanish d15c_243b71de:

    # Z "A hidden place with shelter, food and drinkable water in abundance..."
    Z "Un lugar escondido con refugio, comida y agua potable en abundancia..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2346
translate spanish d15c_b432a3c0:

    # I "Yes, but we have to be careful. It took a lot of work to raise this many plants, and it's a delicate balance."
    I "Sí, pero tenemos que tener cuidado. Se necesitó mucho trabajo para cultivar tantas plantas y es un equilibrio delicado."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2349
translate spanish d15c_5d6e0d83:

    # Z "I suppose that you couldn't depend only on these plants, if that's the case."
    Z "Supongo que no se podría depender sólo de estas plantas, si ese es el caso."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2350
translate spanish d15c_a1f72209:

    # Z "Alright then, let me earn my keep."
    Z "Muy bien, entonces déjame ganarme la vida."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2355
translate spanish d15c_f7dcc5cd:

    # "You collect flowers for some time, taking care not to damage the plants in the process. It's a new experience for you, somehow relaxing..."
    "Recolectas flores durante un tiempo, teniendo cuidado de no dañar las plantas en el proceso. Es una experiencia nueva para ti, de alguna manera relajante..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2358
translate spanish d15c_ea25eb66:

    # Zt "There.. that should be the last one."
    Zt "AhYa está... esta debería ser la última."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2359
translate spanish d15c_74ad3d5e:

    # Zt "This mist is getting so thick..."
    Zt "Esta niebla se está poniendo tan espesa..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2362
translate spanish d15c_5ab3574d:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2363
translate spanish d15c_54ed4e46:

    # Z "Oxygen, she said..."
    Z "Oxígeno, dijo ella..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2366
translate spanish d15c_80e3613e:

    # "You inhale deeply, catching the full strength of the scent of these flowers, something similar to lavender but at the same time alien and new..."
    "Inhalas profundamente, captando toda la fuerza del aroma de estas flores, algo parecido a la lavanda pero al mismo tiempo extraño y nuevo..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2369
translate spanish d15c_a5d746bf:

    # Z "...!"
    Z "¡...!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2370
translate spanish d15c_c5cef2ec:

    # Z "Wow... this is intense... I'm almost getting light-headed."
    Z "Guau... Esto es intenso... Casi me estoy mareando."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2373
translate spanish d15c_287f5332:

    # "For a second you have the oddest of sensations, as if you were choking on too much air, and you cough, caught unaware."
    "Por un segundo tienes una sensación rarísima, como si te ahogaras con demasiado aire, y toses, pillado desprevenido."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2374
translate spanish d15c_15365b8b:

    # "The calming effect that gathering the sturdy petals had on you, accompanied by this sudden intake of new, fresh air, put you at ease."
    "El efecto calmante que tuvo en ti la recolección de los robustos pétalos, acompañado por esta repentina entrada de aire nuevo y fresco, te tranquilizó."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2375
translate spanish d15c_608261ae:

    # "You breathe in again, bending your mind to enjoy the moment of rare, complete peace."
    "Inspiras de nuevo, inclinando tu mente para disfrutar del momento de rara y completa paz."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2378
translate spanish d15c_5a12609a:

    # "As you get up to join [I] once more, the moment passes, and a gust of hot desert wind fills your lungs again."
    "A medida que te levantas para unirte a [I] una vez más, el momento pasa y una ráfaga de viento cálido del desierto llena tus pulmones nuevamente."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2379
translate spanish d15c_9b37ffb1:

    # I "Are you finished?"
    I "¿Terminaste?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2382
translate spanish d15c_ae4b4f5a:

    # Z "I... think so, yeah."
    Z "Yo... creo que sí, sí."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2383
translate spanish d15c_fe6ca6aa:

    # I "You can put the bag next to the other one, I will take care of it later!"
    I "¡Puedes poner la bolsa junto a la otra, ¡yo me ocuparé de ella más tarde!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2386
translate spanish d15c_488d3db5:

    # Z "What do you want to do now?"
    Z "¿Qué quieres hacer ahora?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2389
translate spanish d15c_69441250:

    # I "I was thinking we could take a break up there."
    I "Estaba pensando que podríamos tomarnos un descanso allí arriba."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2392
translate spanish d15c_f5b50dce:

    # Z "Up there? Where does that lead?"
    Z "¿Arriba? ¿A dónde lleva eso?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2395
translate spanish d15c_bebe2839:

    # Z "Oh... right."
    Z "Oh... cierto."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2398
translate spanish d15c_c978a8d0:

    # I "There is a spot up there that is ideal to take a rest."
    I "Hay un lugar allí arriba que es ideal para descansar."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2401
translate spanish d15c_94950b91:

    # Z "I see you like climbing!"
    Z "¡Veo que te gusta escalar!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2404
translate spanish d15c_b93c7774:

    # Z "Alright. Lead the way."
    Z "Está bien. Tú primero."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2407
translate spanish d15c_179b0382:

    # "You climb up the broken pillars of the ancient ruin. As the sun starts to set, the sky starts to darken."
    "Subes por los pilares rotos de las antiguas ruinas. A medida que el sol comienza a ponerse, el cielo comienza a oscurecerse."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2413
translate spanish d15c_5ab3574d_1:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2416
translate spanish d15c_3f650421:

    # Z "Do you need help with something?"
    Z "¿Necesitas ayuda con algo?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2419
translate spanish d15c_f7ba180c:

    # I "Thank you, but I am fine."
    I "Gracias, pero estoy bien."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2425
translate spanish d15c_902f045a:

    # "You look around you, as the sun sets. You've experienced similar moments, sitting atop the ruins of places you have explored or conquered."
    "Miras a tu alrededor mientras se pone el sol. Has experimentado momentos similares, sentado sobre las ruinas de lugares que has explorado o conquistado."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2426
translate spanish d15c_1cd40697:

    # "Every one of those experiences was unique, but this one does seem to stand out."
    "Cada una de esas experiencias fue única, pero ésta parece destacarse."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2427
translate spanish d15c_f8ac1b09:

    # "Maybe it's the effect of the gasses in the cave, maybe it's the unique natural environment, but something of this place feels almost otherworldly."
    "Tal vez sea el efecto de los gases en la cueva, tal vez sea el entorno natural único, pero algo de este lugar parece casi de otro mundo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2428
translate spanish d15c_10b7718b:

    # "Much like a Zone, but still steeped in the real world as the rusty coloured sky demonstrates."
    "Muy parecido a una Zona, pero aún impregnado del mundo real, como lo demuestra el cielo de color oxidado."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2431
translate spanish d15c_2416fb28:

    # "You scan the place for [I], and spot her removing her leathers."
    "Exploras el lugar en busca de [I] y la ves quitándose el mono de cuero."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2434
translate spanish d15c_5018f220_2:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2437
translate spanish d15c_c325f190:

    # I "Oh, um... I didn't think about you being here. I wanted to be a bit more comfortable."
    I "Oh, um... No pensé en que estuvieras aquí. Quería estar un poco más cómoda."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2440
translate spanish d15c_5fb19b6b:

    # I "If that's okay with you..."
    I "Si te parece bien..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2443
translate spanish d15c_f4d3daa9:

    # Z "Of course it is. Just pretend I am not here."
    Z "Por supuesto que me lo parece. Sólo finge que no estoy aquí."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2446
translate spanish d15c_5ab3574d_2:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2447
translate spanish d15c_76d4f6c1:

    # I "I... usually don't let people get close. Not very social, let's say."
    I "Yo... normalmente no dejo que la gente se acerque. No soy muy sociable, que digamos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2448
translate spanish d15c_cf1dbea6:

    # I "I don't really... we don't get visitors."
    I "Realmente no... no recibimos visitas."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2451
translate spanish d15c_ea908f2c:

    # Z "There are worse things than revealing yourself to a friend, and you're still fully dressed."
    Z "Hay cosas peores que mostrarte a un amigo, y aún estás completamente vestida."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2454
translate spanish d15c_4d33be15:

    # I "Yes, you're right."
    I "Sí, tienes razón."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2457
translate spanish d15c_bfe72686:

    # I "And it's not like you haven't seen a lot more than this..."
    I "Y no es que no hayas visto mucho más que esto..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2460
translate spanish d15c_dace167d:

    # Z "True."
    Z "Cierto."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2463
translate spanish d15c_b72925d6:

    # "Your mind goes back to your last visit and you smile at the memory."
    "Tu mente vuelve a tu última visita y sonríes al recordarlo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2464
translate spanish d15c_5ab3574d_3:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2466
translate spanish d15c_24cd75ba:

    # Z "Do you...-"
    Z "¿Tú...-"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2470
translate spanish d15c_1005fd1b:

    # C "Yuna?!"
    C "¡¿Yuna?!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2471
translate spanish d15c_6e037dd7:

    # Z "...?"
    Z "¿...?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2474
translate spanish d15c_26a803bc:

    # C "..."
    C "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2477
translate spanish d15c_e439129f:

    # C "What is... {i}he{/i} doing here...?"
    C "¿Qué está haciendo... {i}él{/i}... aquí...?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2480
translate spanish d15c_4f6cc168:

    # I "Sonmi... there you are..."
    I "Sonmi... Estás aquí..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2483
translate spanish d15c_8290f391:

    # So "Why... Yuna?"
    So "¿Por qué... Yuna?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2486
translate spanish d15c_7934836f:

    # So "What possessed you to bring someone here? Are you out of your mind?"
    So "¿Qué te impulsó a traer a alguien aquí? ¿Estás loca?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2487
translate spanish d15c_8dcebb62:

    # So "You know how dangerous it is to let our guard down! Why not just hand them your weapons too?"
    So "¡Sabes lo peligroso que es bajar la guardia! ¿Por qué no simplemente entregarles tus armas también?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2488
translate spanish d15c_069285d9:

    # I "He... can help us."
    I "Él... puede ayudarnos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2491
translate spanish d15c_9c8b84d0:

    # So "When has anyone ever helped us? We are still prey to them."
    So "¿Cuándo nos ha ayudado alguien? Seguimos siendo presa de ellos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2492
translate spanish d15c_8c71e86f:

    # So "You should know that by now."
    So "Ya deberías saberlo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2495
translate spanish d15c_3e8290a9:

    # I "Sonmi..."
    I "Sonmi..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2496
translate spanish d15c_2c2e3c89:

    # I "He can help us get back home!"
    I "¡Él puede ayudarnos a regresar a casa!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2499
translate spanish d15c_51607195:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2502
translate spanish d15c_94415da5:

    # So "How... how would you know you can trust him."
    So "¿Cómo... cómo sabes que puedes confiar en él?."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2505
translate spanish d15c_dad992b9:

    # I "I just know. I promise. You know I can always tell!"
    I "Sólo lo sé. Te lo prometo. ¡Sabes que siempre puedo saberlo!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2508
translate spanish d15c_93c2f2c8:

    # So "What if you're wrong? What am I going to do then?"
    So "¿Qué pasa si te equivocas? ¿Qué voy a hacer entonces?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2509
translate spanish d15c_5e51df28:

    # So "Why do you care to go back?"
    So "¿Por qué te importa volver?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2512
translate spanish d15c_64b6c42b:

    # I "Not for me, Sonmi. I want you to see it too."
    I "No es para mí, Sonmi. Quiero que tú también lo veas."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2515
translate spanish d15c_0d1e6261:

    # So "You almost died out there, Yuna. Again!"
    So "Casi te mueres ahí fuera, Yuna. ¡Otra vez!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2516
translate spanish d15c_4a33e602:

    # So "For what?!"
    So "¡¿Para qué?!"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2519
translate spanish d15c_1becd21d:

    # So "I am going back to the Wyrd."
    So "Voy a regresar a Wyrd."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2522
translate spanish d15c_94424323:

    # So "I need to think about this."
    So "Tengo que pensar en esto."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2524
translate spanish d15c_3c84b7c7:

    # So "Yuna..."
    So "Yuna..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2527
translate spanish d15c_0613c847:

    # So "I did not want to... shout."
    So "Yo no quería... gritar."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2530
translate spanish d15c_cecb5de6:

    # So "But you keep doing this... first you open the bunker and give it away, and now this... why?"
    So "Pero sigues haciéndolo... primero abres el búnker y lo regalas, y ahora esto... ¿Por qué?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2536
translate spanish d15c_0bff5694:

    # So "Why is it we don't talk anymore?"
    So "¿Por qué ya no nos hablamos?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2539
translate spanish d15c_5018f220_3:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2542
translate spanish d15c_abc23155:

    # "She turns to face you..."
    "Ella se gira para mirarte..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2543
translate spanish d15c_51607195_1:

    # So "..."
    So "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2546
translate spanish d15c_770457c0:

    # So "I will go back out again."
    So "Volveré a salir de nuevo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2552
translate spanish d15c_c0392297:

    # I "Be saf-..."
    I "Ten cuidado-..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2555
translate spanish d15c_5018f220_4:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2558
translate spanish d15c_5ab3574d_4:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2559
translate spanish d15c_a7bfab37:

    # Z "So this is Sonmi."
    Z "Así que esta es Sonmi."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2562
translate spanish d15c_c5336e08:

    # Z "Should I have said something?"
    Z "¿Debería haber dicho algo?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2565
translate spanish d15c_c6497253:

    # I "It's okay. It's not the first time we've argued. I'm happy, actually. She rarely speaks at all since, well... years, really."
    I "Está bien. No es la primera vez que discutimos. Estoy feliz, de hecho. Ella rara vez habla desde, bueno... años, en realidad."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2568
translate spanish d15c_233b3e03:

    # Z "Would you tell me more about her?"
    Z "¿Podrías contarme más sobre ella?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2571
translate spanish d15c_7f525531:

    # Z "What did you mean when you said I can help you get home?"
    Z "¿Qué quisiste decir cuando dijiste que puedo ayudarte a llegar a casa?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2574
translate spanish d15c_08ca9df6:

    # I "Home is where we once used to live."
    Z "¿A qué te referías con que puedo ayudarte a llegar a casa?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2577
translate spanish d15c_c7612970:

    # I "I could try to explain more..."
    I "Podría intentar explicar más..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2580
translate spanish d15c_5018f220_5:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2581
translate spanish d15c_74a726e0:

    # "She reaches out towards you, her meaning unclear..."
    "Te tiende la mano, pero no queda claro qué intenta decir..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2584
translate spanish d15c_4f2cee53:

    # I "Can I..."
    I "Yo puedo..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2585
translate spanish d15c_33ece2bc:

    # I "It's this thing..."
    I "Es esta cosa..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2588
translate spanish d15c_3cf11edf:

    # Z "What do you mean?"
    Z "¿Qué quieres decir?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2591
translate spanish d15c_9a161181:

    # I "Back when we were young, my people, my family..."
    I "Cuando éramos jóvenes, mi gente, mi familia..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2592
translate spanish d15c_41d96437:

    # I "When we would tell each other important things, or stories, we would touch hands."
    I "Cuando nos contábamos cosas o historias importantes, nos tocábamos las manos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2593
translate spanish d15c_0f4a4772:

    # I "[So] used to say she could feel my heartbeat, and tell if I was lying. I am not sure if she was making that up though."
    I "[So] solía decir que podía sentir los latidos de mi corazón y saber si estaba mintiendo. Aunque no estoy segura de si se lo estaba inventando."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2596
translate spanish d15c_1dca2391:

    # I "Do you mind... doing the same?"
    I "¿Te importaría... hacer lo mismo?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2599
translate spanish d15c_48d8fe5e:

    # Z "I remember this. You reached out for me in the barracks as well."
    Z "Recuerdo esto. También me contactaste en el cuartel."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2602
translate spanish d15c_5018f220_6:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2605
translate spanish d15c_fce95215:

    # I "I want to tell you more about our past, and I am more comfortable this way."
    I "Quiero contarte más sobre nuestro pasado y me siento más cómoda así."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2608
translate spanish d15c_3b418ccf:

    # I "I think it's more intimate."
    I "Creo que es más íntimo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2611
translate spanish d15c_c0731b48:

    # I "Through subtle pressures of our fingers, we learned to also convey emotions."
    I "A través de sutiles presiones de nuestros dedos, aprendimos a transmitir también emociones."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2614
translate spanish d15c_7ed22388:

    # I "Now..."
    I "Ahora bien..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2618
translate spanish d15c_e276d76c:

    # I "Close your eyes, please."
    I "Cierra los ojos, por favor."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2624
translate spanish d15c_813f2973:

    # I "Picture a field."
    I "Imagina un campo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2626
translate spanish d15c_4a08cb32:

    # I "Now, a tower, standing tall at its center, surrounded by city ruins, untouched by the passing of time. Similar to the one you know."
    I "Ahora, una torre, erguida en su centro, rodeada de ruinas de la ciudad, intacta por el paso del tiempo. Similar a la que conoces."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2627
translate spanish d15c_e58c6c0f:

    # I "We used to live there, for many decades, observing the changes from a distance."
    I "Vivimos allí durante muchas décadas, observando los cambios desde la distancia."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2629
translate spanish d15c_e9859f27:

    # I "Tribes were settling, building their homes..."
    I "Las tribus se estaban asentando, construyendo sus hogares..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2632
translate spanish d15c_7d796927:

    # I "...but they weren't meant to last forever."
    I "... pero no estaban destinados a durar para siempre."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2635
translate spanish d15c_2d68b787:

    # I "So we watched them vanish."
    I "Así que los vimos desaparecer."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2637
translate spanish d15c_bb152725:

    # I "When more showed up after some time, a different culture, habits, new people trying to survive..."
    I "Cuando después de un tiempo aparecieron más, una cultura diferente, hábitos, gente nueva tratando de sobrevivir..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2640
translate spanish d15c_af9a2124:

    # I "...we watched them too get lost to the desert..."
    I "... los vimos también perderse en el desierto..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2643
translate spanish d15c_bc57316d:

    # I "...leaving behind nothing but rubble and ruins, again."
    I "... dejando atrás nada más que escombros y ruinas, otra vez."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2645
translate spanish d15c_cfa2f860:

    # I "Decades after decades passed, and we saw so many different people come and go..."
    I "Pasaron décadas tras décadas, y vimos a tanta gente diferente ir y venir..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2648
translate spanish d15c_00d79095:

    # I "...as those of us your people like to call elves, outlived all of them."
    I "... como a aquellos de nosotros, tu gente nos gusta llamar a los elfos, sobrevivimos a todos ellos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2651
translate spanish d15c_e9df0afe:

    # I "In time, our only certainty, our only immutable condition was life in the tower."
    I "Con el tiempo, nuestra única certeza, nuestra única condición inmutable fue la vida en la torre."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2653
translate spanish d15c_eee2f052:

    # I "Imagine seeing children and youngsters your age, sometimes even meeting them and becoming friends..."
    I "Imagínate ver a niños y jóvenes de tu edad, a veces incluso conocerlos y hacerse amigos..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2656
translate spanish d15c_f93641cc:

    # I "...and they all age before you, whereas you don't change."
    I "... y todos envejecen antes que tú, mientras que tú no cambias."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2657
translate spanish d15c_e81c938d:

    # I "You see them live their lives, struggle, fight and suffer, but you can't allow yourself to be too close, because your lifespan is counted in centuries."
    I "Los ves vivir sus vidas, luchar, pelear y sufrir, pero no puedes permitirte estar demasiado cerca, porque tu esperanza de vida se cuenta en siglos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2660
translate spanish d15c_e5d63b40:

    # I "So you isolate yourself, you try to detach from the goings on, and you stay away from your window more and more, until, eventually, you stop looking."
    I "Así que te aíslas, intentas despegarte de lo que sucede y te alejas cada vez más de tu ventana, hasta que, finalmente, dejas de mirar."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2663
translate spanish d15c_800a94fd:

    # I "Some of us always said that time is what stops history happening at once...That time is the speed at which the past disappears."
    I "Algunos de nosotros siempre dijimos que el tiempo es lo que impide que la historia suceda de golpe... Ese tiempo es la velocidad con la que el pasado desaparece."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2664
translate spanish d15c_7b17c14b:

    # I "And ultimately, time is all that we had. Time to ourselves, time to read the few books we had for the eleventh time."
    I "Y en última instancia, tiempo es todo lo que teníamos. Tiempo para nosotros mismos, tiempo para leer los pocos libros que teníamos por undécima vez."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2665
translate spanish d15c_8d57565d:

    # I "Time to unlearn how to be in the world."
    I "Es hora de desaprender cómo estar en el mundo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2668
translate spanish d15c_7be0bc60:

    # I "Throughout all this, Sonmi lived knowing only one ever-constant ineffable, which was that lone tower in the city of the dead that we called home."
    I "A lo largo de todo esto, Sonmi vivió sabiendo sólo un inefable siempre constante, que era esa torre solitaria en la ciudad de los muertos a la que llamábamos hogar."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2670
translate spanish d15c_17646382:

    # I "Until one day, all of it ended. The once secure walls were no more."
    I "Hasta que un día todo terminó. Los muros que alguna vez fueron seguros ya no existían."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2671
translate spanish d15c_2e3dcbe6:

    # I "Imagine everything you hold dear, your friends and family, disappearing like the people outside."
    I "Imagina todo lo que aprecias, tus amigos y familiares, desapareciendo como la gente de afuera."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2672
translate spanish d15c_cf47ac47:

    # I "We tried to build a feeling of safety and stability out here in the ruins."
    I "Intentamos crear una sensación de seguridad y estabilidad aquí en las ruinas."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2673
translate spanish d15c_5b6a56d0:

    # I "But the life that has been lost will not come back. And a part of Sonmi is still in the tower, stuck in a need for isolation and safety."
    I "Pero la vida que se ha perdido no volverá. Y una parte de Sonmi todavía está en la torre, atrapada en la necesidad de aislamiento y seguridad."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2682
translate spanish d15c_4ad45e87:

    # I "...I have been trying to find a way to help her out for a long time."
    I "... he estado tratando de encontrar una manera de ayudarla durante mucho tiempo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2685
translate spanish d15c_fc381c50:

    # I "...and... I imagined that she would want to make peace with her memories."
    I "... e... imaginé que ella querría hacer las paces con sus recuerdos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2686
translate spanish d15c_1e87330c:

    # I "It is not the only thing that burdens her... but it could be a start."
    I "No es lo único que la agobia... pero podría ser un comienzo."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2687
translate spanish d15c_0affc75d:

    # I "I figured that if I found a trinket from there, our old home, something tangible for her to remember..."
    I "Pensé que si encontraba una baratija de allí, nuestro antiguo hogar, algo tangible para que ella lo recordara..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2690
translate spanish d15c_5d7f718f:

    # I "Maybe that would help her put the past behind her and look at the present."
    I "Tal vez eso la ayudaría a dejar atrás el pasado y mirar el presente."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2691
translate spanish d15c_885fea03:

    # I "That is why I tried to go back to the tower, by myself, even though I knew the risk was high. That's how I was captured."
    I "Por eso intenté volver a la torre, yo sola, aunque sabía que el riesgo era alto. Así fue como me capturaron."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2694
translate spanish d15c_5018f220_7:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2700
translate spanish d15c_5018f220_8:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2701
translate spanish d15c_7d400ac5:

    # "You realize you locked hands. Her soft fingers feel warm and her touch gentle."
    "Te das cuenta de que os habéis dado la mano. Sus suaves dedos se sienten cálidos y su tacto suave."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2704
translate spanish d15c_fc3eb503:

    # "You let go of each other..."
    "Os soltáis el uno al otro..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2707
translate spanish d15c_e99a5c0a:

    # I "Thank you for saving my life, [persistent.player_name]."
    I "Gracias por salvarme la vida, [persistent.player_name]."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2714
translate spanish d15c_d942918b:

    # Z "[I]..."
    Z "[I]..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2717
translate spanish d15c_ce3a8746:

    # Z "...does she know you were going there for her sake?"
    Z "... ¿sabía ella que ibas allí por ella?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2720
translate spanish d15c_756fbece:

    # I "...No, I don't want her to feel responsible, or guilty."
    I "... No, no quiero que ella se sienta responsable o culpable."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2723
translate spanish d15c_5ab3574d_5:

    # Z "..."
    Z "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2724
translate spanish d15c_216be2d8:

    # Zt "So that is why she was so strongly against my presence here."
    Zt "Por eso ella estaba tan en contra de mi presencia aquí."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2727
translate spanish d15c_2a945c96:

    # Z "Thank you for telling me your story."
    Z "Gracias por contarme tu historia."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2730
translate spanish d15c_5018f220_9:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2736
translate spanish d15c_99989911:

    # Z "It has been a long day..."
    Z "Ha sido un día largo..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2739
translate spanish d15c_3ba354b2:

    # I "It has."
    I "Lo ha sido."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2742
translate spanish d15c_ed62b37d:

    # I "If you don't want to ride back in the dark, you can sleep in my bed, like last time."
    I "Si no quieres regresar en la oscuridad, puedes dormir en mi cama, como la última vez."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2745
translate spanish d15c_6e8bd054:

    # Z "Won't that make your friend even more angry?"
    Z "¿Eso no enfadará aún más a tu amiga?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2748
translate spanish d15c_b9a2da0d:

    # I "I doubt she will be back before a day, or maybe two."
    I "Dudo que regrese antes de un día, o tal vez dos."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2751
translate spanish d15c_71eff187:

    # Z "I see. Where will you sleep? Or won't you?"
    Z "Ya veo. ¿Dónde dormirás tú? ¿O no lo harás?"

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2754
translate spanish d15c_220662af:

    # I "I will... outside. Like last time."
    I "Lo haré... afuera. Como la última vez."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2755
translate spanish d15c_3c2cd639:

    # I "I like to be in the water... it makes me feel weightless. I like that a lot."
    I "Me gusta estar en el agua... me hace sentir ingrávida. Eso me gusta mucho."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2758
translate spanish d15c_1108a587:

    # Z "Alright. I will spend the night then, and leave first thing in the morning."
    Z "Está bien. Pasaré la noche entonces y me iré a primera hora de la mañana."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2759
translate spanish d15c_526540e6:

    # Z "I will try not to disturb you, when I leave. Also..."
    Z "Intentaré no molestarte cuando me vaya. Además..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2762
translate spanish d15c_1091cb8b:

    # Z "I will get you both back there, somehow. Back to your tower."
    Z "Os llevaré a las dos de vuelta, de alguna manera. De vuelta a vuestra torre."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2768
translate spanish d15c_5018f220_10:

    # I "..."
    I "..."

# game/scripts/day15.rpy:2777
translate spanish d15c_abebf667:

    # "After spending the night in her bed, you make your way back home early in the morning..."
    "Después de pasar la noche en su cama, vuelves a casa por la mañana temprano..."

