    # game/scripts/day15.rpy:1293
    old "The surprising visit of Nadia and Rabiah was quite pleasant, especially because it was the first time I have seen them without Omar at their side.\nIt turns out that Rabiah did come out of her shell a bit.\nShe seems more content and less frustrated, even in my presence."
    new "La sorprendente visita de Nadia y Rabiah fue bastante agradable, especialmente porque fue la primera vez que las vi sin Omar a su lado.\nResulta que Rabiah salió un poco de su caparazón.\nParece más contenta y menos frustrada, incluso en mi presencia."

    # game/scripts/day15.rpy:2005
    old "I would like that."
    new "Eso me gustaría."

    # game/scripts/day15.rpy:2005
    old "You've never done anything with boys?"
    new "¿Nunca has hecho nada con chicos?"

    # game/scripts/day15.rpy:2765
    old "It was the first time I have seen {I}'s friend; her name is Sonmi. White hair, pointy elven ears and a young face.\nThe history these two share is slowly being revealed to me, and apparently, I will play a part in rediscovering it.\nThere is an old Tower, similar to those of the mutants lead by Fangs.\nI could bring them there, when the time is right."
    new "Fue la primera vez que vi a la amiga de {I}; su nombre es Sonmi. Pelo blanco, orejas puntiagudas de elfa y un rostro joven.\nLa historia que comparten estas dos se está revelando lentamente ante mí y, al parecer, jugaré un papel en redescubrirla.\nHay una antigua torre, similar a las de los mutantes liderados por Fangs.\nPodría llevarlas allí cuando sea el momento adecuado."

